Discover Our Neighborhood – Hollywood, CA.

Let’s face it—there is just no place on Earth quite like Hollywood. Yes, this is the birthplace of American cinema, but there is so much more here, starting with the famous California sunshine and, of course, a mecca of music industry professionals. Right next door to Loews Hollywood is the famous Hollywood & Highland. It’s a great choice for shopping, people-watching or enjoying a few games of bowling. This is also where the famous Dolby Theater, home of the Academy Awards, is located. Love hoops? You’ll want to check out a Lakers game as well.

No matter what you like to do, you’ll find a myriad of things to do around the Loews Hollywood Hotel during your star for the Vocal Star music competition.
